0It's%20an%20experimental%20effort%20to%20reimagine%20what%20AI%20agents%20can%20be%20in%20the%20future.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20universal%20agent%20that%20will%20be%20useful%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20DeepMind%20chief%20Demis%20Hassabis%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20at%20the%20test%20location%2C%20Google%20let%20four%3Cspan%3E%20journalists%20at%20a%20time%20into%20little%20demo%20booths.%20Before%20we%20went%20in%2C%20while%20waiting%20in%20line%2C%20two%20members%20of%20the%20Project%20Astra%20team%20from%20DeepMind%20walked%20us%20through%20how%20to%20use%20the%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20described%20four%20modes%20for%20us%20to%20try%20out%3A%20Storyteller%2C%20Pictionary%2C%20Free-Form%20and%20Alliteration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da8137ba-91b0-4c66-98c8-afa864214416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFree-Form%20mode%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20tried%20Free-Form%20mode.%20Max%20Cherney%2C%20a%20journalist%20from%20Reuters%2C%20held%20up%20a%20Google-provided%20Android%20phone%20and%20pointed%20the%20camera%20at%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BDescribe%20his%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20Max%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20model%20reviewed%20the%20phone's%20live%20video%20and%20said%20I%20was%20wearing%20casual%20clothes.%20An%20accurate%2C%20solid%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20dancing%20and%20Max%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20he%20doing%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20responded%20incorrectly%2C%20kind%20of.%20It%20said%20I%20had%20put%20on%20sunglasses.%20Which%20was%20true%2C%20because%20I'd%20put%20on%20some%20sunnies%20to%20dance.%20But%20it%20didn't%20spot%20the%20dancing.%20Admittedly%2C%20I%20was%20dancing%20badly%2C%20so%20maybe%20the%20AI%20model%20gets%20a%20pass%20on%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246b71491-fcb9-46c7-88a9-863d36161877%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20stock%20quotes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20Max%20asked%20Gemini%20to%20critique%20my%20attire%2C%20because%20he%20wanted%20Gemini%20to%20do%20some%20analysis%20and%20share%20a%20point%20of%20view.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20AI%20model%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20provide%20stock%20quotes%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20We%20all%20stopped%20as%20the%20AI%20magic%20had%20abruptly%20ended.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250804134-5575-4c26-8b42-8b85028b0e7d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20car%20and%20a%20story%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20then%20moved%20to%20a%20large%20touch%20screen%20that%20offered%20the%20four%20modes%20to%20try.%20I%20chose%20Pictionary.%20I%20drew%20a%20really%20bad%20car%2C%20and%20Gemini%20said%20%26quot%3Bthat%20looks%20like%20a%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20it%20to%20put%20the%20vehicle%20in%20an%20interesting%20story.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sleek%2C%20blue%20car%20sped%20down%20the%20highway%2C%20a%20lonely%20traveler%20on%20a%20moonlit%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20the%20car%20drive%20into%20a%20marketplace%20and%20Gemini%20said%20doing%20that%20would%20be%20unsafe%20in%20reality%2C%20but%20it%20could%20make%20a%20good%20story%20plot%20twist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIs%20that%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20drew%20a%20table%20of%20fruit%20at%20the%20market.%20It%20was%20even%20worse%20than%20the%20car.%20Then%20I%20said%20someone%20should%20steal%20fruit%20in%20the%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAh%2C%20a%20fruit%20thief%20adds%20an%20interesting%20twist!%20Are%20they%20getting%20away%20with%20it%20so%20far%3F%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20demo%20ended%20and%20we%20were%20ushered%20out%20of%20the%20booth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223597ac07-eb91-4f5d-9240-1200c41614fd%5C%22%3EGregory%20Wayne%20and%20Captain%20Cook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20outside%2C%20I%20ran%20into%20Gregory%20Wayne%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Project%20Astra.%20He's%20been%20at%20DeepMind%20for%20about%20a%20decade%20and%20we%20discussed%20the%20origins%20on%20Project%20Astra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20he's%20been%20fascinated%20by%20how%20humans%20communicate%20using%20language.%20Not%20just%20written%20and%20spoken%20words%2C%20but%20all%20the%20other%20forms%20of%20communication%20that%20make%20human%20interaction%20so%20rich%20and%20satisfying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20recounted%20a%20story%20about%20when%20Captain%20Cook%20arrived%20in%20Tierra%20del%20Fuego%20and%20met%20the%20inhabitants.%20They%20did%20not%20speak%20the%20same%20language%2C%20so%20they%20communicated%20through%20actions%2C%20such%20as%20picking%20up%20sticks%20and%20throwing%20them%20to%20the%20side%2C%20which%20signified%20that%20Cook%20and%20his%20crew%20were%20welcome.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWayne%20and%20his%20colleagues%20were%20fascinated%20by%20the%20story%20because%20it%20showed%20all%20the%20other%20ways%20that%20humans%20can%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20beyond%20what%20people%20are%20taught%20to%20do%20through%20written%20words%20and%20speaking%20aloud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213e3fbd3-bbdc-41db-93b5-21faf55068b6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20chatbots%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20what%20inspired%20Project%20Astra%2C%20Wayne%20said.%20It's%20all%20about%20going%20beyond%20what%20chatbots%20do%20right%20now%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20understanding%20written%20and%20spoken%20words%20and%20conducting%20simple%20back-and-forth%20conversations%2C%20where%20the%20computer%20says%20something%2C%20then%20the%20human%20does%2C%20then%20the%20computer%20again%20and%20so%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20goals%20of%20Project%20Astra%20is%20to%20get%20AI%20models%20to%20comprehend%20many%20of%20the%20other%20things%20going%20on%20around%20text%20and%20speech-based%20communication.%20That%20might%20be%20hand%20signals%2C%20or%20the%20context%20of%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20moment%20of%20the%20conversation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20future%2C%20this%20could%20include%20something%20like%20an%20AI%20model%20or%20agent%20spotting%20something%20in%20the%20background%20of%20a%20video%20feed%20and%20alerting%20the%20human%20in%20the%20conversation.%20That%20might%20be%20a%20bicycle%20approaching%2C%20or%20telling%20the%20user%20when%20a%20traffic%20light%20changes%20color.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20options%20are%20endless%2C%20and%20also%20include%20an%20AI%20model%20understanding%2C%20through%20kind%20of%20reading%20the%20room%2C%20that%20it%20should%20stop%20talking%20and%20let%20the%20human%20say%20something.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263c7da93-ec42-4244-b86b-cafd729b18e6%5C%22%3ESuperEvilMegaCorp%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20told%20Wayne%20about%20the%20slightly%20disappointing%20moment%20when%20Gemini%20didn't%20critique%20my%20clothes%20and%20instead%20said%20it%20couldn't%20provide%20stock%20quotes%20right%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20immediately%20looked%20at%20my%20T-shirt%2C%20which%20has%20a%20real%20startup%20logo%20on%20it%20that%20reads%20%26quot%3BSuperEvilMegaCorp.%26quot%3B%20Wayne%20theorized%20that%20Gemini%20saw%20the%20corporation%20name%20and%20guessed%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20know%20financial%20information%20about%20this%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuperEvilMegaCorp%20is%20a%20gaming%2