ial%20combat%20training%20course%20that%20pits%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20aircraft%2C%20often%20from%20multiple%20nations%2C%20against%20large-scale%20and%20realistic%20threats%20meant%20to%20simulate%20a%20real%20near-peer%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20Germany%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationist.com%2F2012%2F06%2F21%2Frf-alaska-12-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20150%20Airmen%20and%20eight%20Eurofighter%20Typhoons%20from%20JG%2074%2C%20or%20the%20Luftwaffe's%2074th%20Tactical%20Air%20Force%20Wing%2C%20to%20Eielson%20AFB%20in%20Alaska%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20missions%20over%20two%20weeks.%20Included%20among%20them%20was%20a%20series%20of%20close-range%20Basic%20Fighter%20Maneuver%20(BFM)%20drills%20with%20America's%20Raptors.%20BFM%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20fighter-pilot%20parlance%20for%20dog%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20exercises%20were%20over%2C%20Germany's%20Eurofighter%20pilots%20arrived%20at%202012's%20Farnborough%20International%20Air%20Show%2C%20where%20they%20were%20quick%20to%20discuss%20their%20victories%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fblog%2Fwhy-america-never-sold-the-f-22-raptor-to-foreign-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EF-22%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20David%20Cenciotti's%20coverage%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationist.com%2F2012%2F07%2F13%2Ffia12-typhoon-raptor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EThe%20Aviationist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Germany's%20Typhoon%20pilots%20explained%20that%20when%20the%20F-22%20was%20flying%20with%20external%20fuel%20tanks%20attached%20and%20fighting%20within%20visual%20range%2C%20Typhoons%20were%20often%20able%20to%20outclass%20the%20Raptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c235920-f48a-4729-9108-15c0f939e590%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20compare%20to%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22German%20Air%20Force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20in%20the%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643cd44b4abc992e8c9848f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerman%20Air%20Force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20during%20a%20media%20day.%3Cp%3EPiroschka%20van%20de%20Wouw%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20generational%20differences%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fblog%2Fthe-king-is-dead-why-would-america-want-to-retire-the-f-22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EF-22%20Raptor%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20actually%20have%20a%20number%20of%20things%20in%20common.%20They%20were%20both%20originally%20designed%20to%20serve%20as%20air%20superiority%20fighters%20born%20out%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurofighter.com%2Fadvantages%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEurofighter%2520Typhoon%2520has%2520an%2520unparalleled%2Coperations%2520in%2520all%2520weather%2520conditions.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETyphoon%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20taking%20to%20the%20skies%20in%201994%20and%20the%20F-22%20following%20behind%20in%201997.%20Likewise%2C%20both%20fighters%20ultimately%20entered%20service%20in%20the%20early-to-mid%202000s%2C%20with%20the%20Typhoon%20entering%20active%20duty%20in%202003%20and%20the%20Raptor%2C%20once%20again%2C%20following%20behind%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20these%20aircraft%20being%20designed%20at%20around%20the%20same%20time%20to%20serve%20in%20similar%20capacities%2C%20they%20differ%20dramatically%20in%20how%20they%20go%20about%20accomplishing%20their%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-22%20Raptor%20was%20always%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20revolution%20in%20airpower%2C%20leaning%20heavily%20into%20America's%20groundbreaking%20stealth%20technology%20to%20produce%20what%20was%20%E2%80%94%20and%20remains%20%E2%80%94%20the%20stealthiest%20operational%20fighter%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20planet.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20stealth%20that%20makes%20the%20Raptor%20a%20capable%20platform.%20It%20also%20boasts%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20sensor%20fusion%20and%20advanced%20avionics%20that%20allow%20for%20an%20extreme%20degree%20of%20situational%20awareness%20while%20reducing%20cognitive%20load%20for%20the%20pilot.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20F-22's%20onboard%20computers%20allow%20the%20pilot%20to%20devote%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20fight%20and%20less%20to%20operating%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20flying%20the%20Raptor%2C%20you're%20not%20thinking%20about%20flying%20the%20Raptor%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20F-22%20pilot%20Randy%20Gordon%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn068fel-W9I%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Electure%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20gave%20at%20MIT%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20thinking%20about%20employing%20the%20Raptor.%20Flying%20is%20secondary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20F-22%20isn't%20all%20about%20stealth%20and%20sensor%20fusion.%20It%20also%20incorporates%20elements%20of%20what%20might%20be%20considered%204th-generation%20dogfighting%20design%3A%20like%20thrust%20vector%20control%20or%20the%20ability%20to%20orient%20its%20jet%20nozzles%20independent%20of%20the%20airframe%20to%20perform%20incredibly%20aerobatic%20maneuvers%2C%20a%20high%20thrust-to-weight%20ratio%2C%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gd-ots.com%2Farmaments%2Faircraft-guns-gun-systems%2Ff22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EM61A2%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2020mm%20Gatling%20gun%20that%20can%20fire%20its%20onboard%20480%20rounds%20at%20a%20blistering%20rate%20of%206%2C000%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224273%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-22%20Raptor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e6bea496242f0019e8746d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222849%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EF-22%20Raptor%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Lt.%20Sam%20Eckholm%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaptor%20has%20vector%20thrust%3A%20Typhoon%20doesn't%2C%26quot%3B%20RAF%20Typhoon%20pilot%20and%20squadron%20commander%20Rich%20Wells%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff-22-wont-win-a-dogfight-thrust-vectoring-raptor-typhoon-eurofighter-2013-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Breaking%20Defense%20in%202013.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20aircraft%20can%20do%2C%20it's%20incredible.%20The%20Typhoon%20just%20doesn't%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20it%20usually%20carries%20a%20total%20of%20eight%20weapons%20internally%20(six%20AMRAAMs%20and%20two%20AIM-9%20Sidewinders)%2C%20it%20can%20be%20fitted%20with%20four%20external%20pylon%20stations%20for%20additional%20munitions%20when%20it's%20tired%20of%20speaking%20softly%20and%20decides%20to%20become%20its%20own%20big%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20F-22%20bridges%20two%20combat%20philosophies%20offering%20such%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20stealth%20and%20situational%20awareness%20that%20it%20can%20win%20most%20fights%20before%20the%20opponent%20even%20knows%20that%20it's%20there%2C%20alongside%20a%20highly%20respectable%20slew%20of%20traditional%20dogfighting%20traits%20that%20allow%20it%20to%20stand%20and%20swing%20with%20the%20most%20dynamic%20hotrod%20dogfighters%20of%20the%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20wasn't%20aiming%20to%20reinvent%20the%20existing%20air%20superiority%20model%2C%20so%20much%20as%20to%20perfect%20it%20as%20it%20was.%20Its%20delta-wing%20design%2C%20a%20shape%20nearly%20adopted%20by%20the%20F-22's%20defunct%20bomber%20sibling%2C%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmegaprojects.net%2Fplanes%2Feurofighter-typhoon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehigh%20degree%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20subsonic%20maneuverability%20alongside%20increased%20lift%20and%20range.%20The%20design%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20materials%20that%20make%20up%20the%20Typhoon%2C%20all%20lend%20it%20a%20higher%20degree%20of%20stealth%20than%20you%20might%20find%20in%20most%20comparably%20advanced%204th-generation%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmegaprojects.net%2Fplanes%2Feurofighter-typhoon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Eurofighter%20promotional%20materials%3A%20The%20aircraft%20is%20built%20with%20advanced%20composite%20materials%20to%20deliver%20a%20low%20radar%20profile%20and%20strong%20airframe.%20Only%2015%25%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20surface%20is%20metal%2C%20delivering%20stealth%20operation%20and%20protection%20from%20radar-based%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224112%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20of%20the%20german%20airforce%20pictured%20on%20September%2010%2C%202014%2C%20over%20Estonia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603252116bde8d4ead26a07%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20of%20the%20german%20airforce%20pictured%20on%20September%2010%2C%202014%2C%20over%20Estonia.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Wiegold%2FPhotothek%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20fighters%2C%20including%20the%20F-22%2C%20the%20Typhoon%20also%20leverages%20electronic%20warfare%20capabilities%20to%20obscure%20its%20radar%20return.%20And%20unlike%20the%20maintenance-heavy%20Raptor%2C%20the%20Typhoon%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20easy%20to%20maintain%2C%20assembled%20out%20of%2015%20interchangeable%20modules%20to%20minimize%20repair%20time.%20When%20up%20close%20and%20personal%2C%20the%20Typhoon's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmegaprojects.net%2Fplanes%2Feurofighter-typhoon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMauser%20BK27mm%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20gun%20fires%20at%20either%201%2C000%20or%201%2C700%20rounds%20per%20minute%2C%20with%20150%20rounds%20carried%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20entering%20service%2C%20the%20Typhoon%20has%20matured%20into%20an%20extremely%20capable%20multi-role%20platform%2C%20leaving%20its%20air%20superiority%20roots%20behind%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20well-rounded%20fighters%20in%20service%20today%2C%20leveraging%20its%2013%20hard%20points%20for%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20mission%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Eurofighter%20is%20certainly%2C%20as%20far%20as%20smoothness%20of%20controls%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20pull%20(and%20sustain%20high%20G%20forces)%2C%20very%20impressive%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FNews%2FArticle-Display%2FArticle%2F134781%2Fcsaf-raptor-eurofighter-complementary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexplained%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gen.%20John%20P.%20Jumper%2C%20former%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20and%20among%20the%20few%20pilots%20to%20have%20seat%20time%20in%20both%20the%20Raptor%20and%20Typhoon.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20what%20it%20was%20designed%20to%20do%2C%20especially%20the%20version%20I%20flew%2C%20with%20the%20avionics%2C%20the%20color%20moving%20map%20displays%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20all%20absolutely%20top-notch.%20The%20maneuverability%20of%20the%20airplane%20in%20close-in%20combat%20was%20also%20very%20impressive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Typhoons%20pair%20of%20Eurojet%20EJ200%20afterburning%20turbofan%20engines%20aren't%20quite%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Raptor's%2C%20propelling%20the%20Eurofighter%20to%20a%20top%20speed%20of%20Mach%202%2C%20vice%20the%20Raptors%202.25%20%E2%80%94%20but%20top%20speed%20doesn't%20mean%20much%20in%20a%20fight%2C%20and%20the%20Eurofighter's%20comparatively%20lower%20weight%20allows%20for%20a%20better%20thrust-to-weight%20ratio%20for%20the%20Typhoon%20(in%20its%20interceptor%20configuration)%20than%20a%20similarly%20equipped%20Raptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285a0e285-6b21-4574-ab84-b75717b28161%5C%22%3EF-22%20vs.%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%3A%20What%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20exercises%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222550%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20US%20Air%20Force's%20F-22%20Raptor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63dd67cee33c4000193ae74c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force's%20F-22%20Raptor.%3Cp%3EMai%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20many%20details%20remain%20murky%2C%20there%20are%20some%20things%20we%20know%20for%20sure%20about%20these%202012%20dogfight%20exercises.%20Based%20on%20pilot%20statements%2C%20we%20know%20that%20at%20least%20some%20(if%20not%20all)%20of%20them%20were%20one-on-one%20engagements.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20they%20occurred%20within%20visual%20range%20with%20a%20number%20of%20reports%20stating%20that%20the%20Raptor%20was%20carrying%20stealth%20(and%20aerobatics)%20hindering%20external%20fuel%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20distinction%20is%20essential%20because%20it%20means%20the%20fighting%20began%20under%20a%20forced%20pretense%20that%20effectively%20neutered%20the%20Raptor's%20greatest%20strength%3A%20its%20ability%20to%20use%20stealth%20and%20situational%20awareness%20to%20dictate%20how%20an%20engagement%20begins%20and%2C%20if%20the%20reports%20of%20fuel%20tanks%20are%20true%2C%20its%20aerobatic%20maneuverability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20real%20life%2C%20F-22%20pilots%20would%20almost%20certainly%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20Typhoon%20before%20the%20Typhoon%20was%20aware%20of%20it%2C%20allowing%20the%20Raptor%20to%20put%20itself%20into%20an%20advantageous%20position%20before%20the%20fighting%20began%20(or%20simply%20taking%20out%20the%20Typhoon%20from%20beyond%20visual%20range).%20And%20it%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20no%20pilot%20would%20dogfight%20for%20their%20lives%20with%20external%20fuel%20tanks%20still%20hanging%20from%20their%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20exercise%20is%20common%20in%20military%20training%2C%20however%2C%20and%20could%20be%20compared%20to%20offensive%20and%20defensive%20positions%20in%20scholastic%20wrestling.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthomasdalewrestling.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F4%2F1%2F9%2F9%2F41997795%2Fwrestling_101_the_basics_part_2.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eneutral%20start%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20wrestling%20begins%20with%20both%20athletes%20on%20their%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20this%20would%20be%20like%20two%20fighters%20flying%20into%20an%20exercise%20in%20the%20same%20way%20they%20might%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%20a%20defensive%20(or%20disadvantaged)%20position%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20when%20one%20wrestler%20begins%20the%20period%20on%20their%20hands%20and%20knees%2C%20with%20their%20opponent%20next%20to%20them%20on%20one%20knee%20with%20an%20arm%20over%20their%20back%20(the%20advantage).%20In%20the%20case%20of%20these%20specific%20exercises%2C%20the%20F-22%20played%20the%20role%20of%20the%20disadvantaged%20wrestler%20starting%20from%20its%20knees%20%E2%80%94%20playing%20to%20the%20Eurofighter's%20strengths%2C%20rather%20than%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22German%20air%20force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c4a135fdde8676c92711fa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20German%20air%20force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20taxis%20toward%20the%20runway%20at%20Eielson%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Alaska%20before%20departing%20for%20a%20combat-training%20mission%2C%20June%2011%2C%202012.%3Cp%3ETech%20Sgt.%20Michael%20Holzworth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20like%20in%20wrestling%2C%20we%20should%20note%20that%20starting%20in%20a%20defensive%20or%20disadvantaged%20position%20isn't%20an%20excuse%20for%20losing.%20It's%20just%20part%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20allowances%20were%20also%20made%20for%20the%20Eurofighter%20before%20the%20fighting%20began.%20While%20the%20F-22%20was%20carrying%20external%20fuel%20tanks%20that%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20compromised%20both%20its%20aerobatic%20and%20stealth%20performance%2C%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20that%20participated%20in%20one-on-one%20dogfights%20against%20the%20Raptor%20was%20allowed%20to%20fly%20not%20only%20without%20fuel%20tanks%2C%20but%20without%20any%20external%20munitions%20at%20all.%20This%20not%20only%20improved%20the%20Typhoon's%20maneuverability%2C%20but%20it%20also%20couldn't%20happen%20in%20a%20real%20fight%20lest%20the%20Eurofighter%20be%20left%20with%20nothing%20but%20its%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20two%20mornings%20where%20we%20flew%20against%20them%201v1.%20We%20pulled%20off%20all%20the%20tanks%20to%20get%20the%20most%20alpha%20%5Bangle%20of%20attack%5D%3B%20the%20Eurofighter%20really%20is%20an%20animal%20with%20no%20tanks%2C%26quot%3B%20Germany's%20Maj.%20Marc%20Gruene%2C%20one%20of%20the%20pilots%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20drills%2C%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20of%20each%20fighter%20participated%20in%20these%20drills%2C%20what%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement%20were%2C%20and%20what%20the%20final%20kill%20ratios%20for%20each%20fighter%20were%20are%20all%20details%20that%20neither%20nation%20has%20disclosed%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20claims%20made%20online.%20While%20these%20claims%20haven't%20been%20confirmed%2C%20they%20all%20report%20more%20wins%20for%20the%20F-22%20than%20the%20Eurofighter%2C%20but%20F-22s%20clearly%20took%20home%20some%20losses%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20Eurofighter%20Typhoons%20come%20equipped%20with%20both%20a%20helmet-mounted%20targeting%20system%20to%20engage%20enemy%20fighters%20off-boresight%20(without%20aiming%20the%20nose%20of%20the%20aircraft%20at%20them)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20PIRATE%20infrared%20search%20and%20track%20(IRST)%20system%20that's%20potentially%20capable%20of%20spotting%20stealth%20fighters%20at%20distances%20as%20great%20as%2030%20miles%20out.%20This%20would%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20advantage%20over%20the%20F-22%20%E2%80%94%20which%20carries%20neither%20capability%20to%20date%20%E2%80%94%20but%20at%20the%20time%20of%20these%20dogfight%20exercises%2C%20these%20systems%20were%20still%20being%20rolled%20out%20to%20Germany's%20Air%20Force%2C%20and%20the%20Typhoons%20that%20participated%20in%20the%20drills%20did%20not%20have%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9afd94e-d950-49f0-89d7-11aa69a66d3c%5C%22%3EWhat%20happened%20when%20the%20F-22%20and%20Eurofighter%20squared%20off%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5UUFcjM9YUA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22F-22%20VS%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20%E2%80%94%20What%20really%20happened%20in%20these%20dogfights%3F%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20German%20pilots%2C%20once%20the%20fighting%20began%2C%20the%20F-22's%20thrust-vector%20control%20(TVC)%20actually%20hindered%20the%20Raptor%2C%20rather%20than%20helping%20it%20when%20sparring%20in%20close%20quarters%20with%20the%20Typhoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20key%20is%20to%20get%20as%20close%20as%20possible%20to%20the%20F-22%20and%20stay%20there.%20They%20didn't%20expect%20us%20to%20turn%20so%20aggressively%2C%26quot%3B%20Gruene%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2012%2F07%2Ff-22-germans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Combat%20Aircraft%20magazine%20back%20in%202012.%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you%20get%20to%20the%20merge%E2%80%A6%20the%20Typhoon%20doesn't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20fear%20the%20F-22.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(The%20Merge%2C%20for%20clarification's%20sake%2C%20isn't%20just%20the%20name%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themerge.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egreat%20aviation%20newsletter%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20also%20what%20fighter%20pilots%20call%20it%20when%20two%20fighters%20meet%20head-on%20in%20a%20close-quarters%20pass.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETVC%20does%20allow%20a%20fighter%20to%20perform%20extreme%20maneuvers%2C%20but%20they%20come%20at%20a%20high%20cost.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fblog%2Fcan-the-f-35-dogfight-the-truth-behind-the-infamous-2015-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edogfight%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20airspeed%20is%20life%2C%20and%20the%20exotic%20displays%20TVC%20allows%20all%20scrub%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20it.%20When%20the%20F-22%20uses%20its%20thrust-vectoring%20nozzles%20to%20turn%20on%20a%20dime%2C%20the%20jet%20is%20vulnerable%20until%20it%20can%20regain%20airspeed.%20If%20it%20doesn't%20manage%20to%20score%20a%20kill%20immediately%20after%20performing%20such%20a%20maneuver%2C%20the%20Raptor%20becomes%20easy%20prey%20until%20its%20powerful%20pair%20of%20F-119-PW-100%20turbofan%20engines%20can%20get%20all%2070%2C000%20pounds%20of%20fighter%20moving%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20was%20explained%20by%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationist.com%2F2013%2F02%2F21%2Fraptor-vs-typhoon-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eunnamed%20Eurofighter%20test%20pilot%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Cenciotti%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20'defensive'%20and%20your%20aircraft%20has%20Thrust%20Vectoring%2C%20you%20can%20possibly%20outturn%20your%20enemy%2C%20but%20that%20most%20likely%20won't%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20great%20idea%3A%20an%20energy%20fighter%20like%20the%20Typhoon%20will%20conveniently%20'use%20the%20vertical'%20to%20retain%20energy%20and%20aggressively%20reposition%20for%20a%20missile%20or%20gun%20shot.%20Also%20the%20subsequent%20acceleration%20will%20be%20extremely%20time%20(and%20fuel)%20consuming%2C%20giving%20your%20opponent%20the%20opportunity%20to%20tail%20chase%20you%20forever%2C%20exploiting%20all%20its%20short%20range%20weapon%20array.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20on%20the%20offensive%2C%20using%20TVC%20to%20quickly%20orient%20the%20nose%20of%20your%20fighter%20toward%20the%20enemy%20isn't%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20either.%20Because%20aggressive%20maneuvers%20strip%20the%20fighter%20of%20energy%2C%20you%20may%20score%20a%20kill%20against%20the%20opponent%20in%20front%20of%20you%2C%20but%20you're%20left%20vulnerable%20to%20any%20others%20nearby.%20This%20inherent%20issue%20with%20thrust%20vectoring%20combat%20tactics%20is%20really%20why%20no%20other%20American%20fighters%20are%20equipped%20with%20it%2C%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20Raptor%20pilots%20themselves%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn068fel-W9I%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewill%20tell%20you%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20real%20benefit%20of%20TVC%20in%20their%20aircraft%20is%20maintaining%20a%20degree%20of%20maneuverability%20while%20flying%20at%20a%20high%20angle%20of%20attack%20when%20control%20surfaces%20aren't%20as%20effective%2C%20rather%20than%20performing%20air%20show%20maneuvers%20in%20a%20dogfight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de930fef-f503-4e79-8898-8f9a517dbaaf%5C%22%3EAt%20least%20two%20Eurofighters%20scored%20kills%20against%20F-22s%E2%80%A6%20but%20there's%20more%20to%20this%20story%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Eurofighters%20during%20takeoff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643cebab4abc992e8c985c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22592%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENATO%20Secretary%20General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%20sits%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20Eurofighter%20on%20take-off%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Tactical%20Air%20Wing%2073%20%26quot%3BSteinhoff.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBernd%20W%C3%BCstneck%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20for%20sure%20that%20at%20least%20some%20(likely%20two)%20Eurofighters%20actually%20scored%20notional%20kills%20against%20their%20F-22%20opponents%20in%20these%20drills.%20That%20story%20was%20quickly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2Fblogs%2Fheadlines%2F2012%2F07%2Ff-22-fighter-loses-79-billion-advantage-in-dogfights-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epicked%20up%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20news%20outlets%20around%20the%20world%2C%20eager%20for%20a%20story%20about%20America's%20expensive%20Raptor%20failing%20to%20live%20up%20to%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20don't%20know%2C%20however%2C%20is%20how%20many%20kills%20Raptors%20scored%20against%20Typhoons%2C%20though%20it%20seems%20clear%20from%20official%20statements%20that%20the%20number%20was%20definitely%20not%20zero.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20story%20wasn't%20that%20Raptors%20consistently%20lost%20to%20Eurofighters%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20that%20sometimes%20they%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20that%20mean%2C%20exactly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20aviation%20buffs%20start%20squaring%20off%20in%20the%20comments%20sections%20below%20articles%20and%20videos%20about%20their%20favorite%20(or%20least%20favorite)%20fighter%20platforms%2C%20it%20usually%20doesn't%20take%20long%20for%20the%20discourse%20to%20stop%20sounding%20like%20a%20well-informed%20debate%20and%20start%20sounding%20like%203rd%20graders%20arguing%20about%20whose%20dad%20can%20beat%20up%20who's.%20The%20complex%20context%20of%20air%20combat%20gives%20way%20to%20oversimplification%20and%20hyperbole%20until%20everything%20devolves%20into%20ad%20hominem%20attacks%20and%20seemingly%20made-up%20and%20uncitable%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20I%20say%3F%20Airplane%20folks%20go%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20however%2C%20reasonable%20arguments%20to%20be%20made%20from%20both%20sides%20of%20this%20debate%2C%20which%20I'll%20try%20to%20capture%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288f30763-a1f5-4d53-abdc-d4fa0b984c53%5C%22%3EThe%20Raptor-fan%20argument%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-22%20Raptor%20fighter%20jet%20performs%20during%20the%20Seoul%20International%20Aerospace%20and%20Defense%20Exhibition.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643cf03f27898f532d7a140%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-22%20Raptor%20fighter%20jet%20performs%20during%20the%20Seoul%20International%20Aerospace%20and%20Defense%20Exhibition.%3Cp%3EChris%20Jung%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20the%20Raptor%20camp%20will%20contend%20that%20exercises%20like%20these%2C%20with%20their%20contrived%20circumstances%20and%20intentionally%20one-sided%20rules%20of%20engagement%20may%20be%20good%20for%20training%2C%20but%20they're%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationist.com%2F2012%2F07%2F13%2Ffia12-typhoon-raptor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epoor%20measure%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20fighter's%20actual%20performance%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20broader%20context.%20The%20very%20nature%20of%20these%20exercises%20set%20out%20to%20put%20the%20Raptor%20at%20a%20disadvantage%2C%20eliminating%20the%20platform's%20greatest%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20its%20stealth%20and%20beyond-visual%20range%20capabilities%2C%20in%20favor%20of%20an%20old-fashioned%20shoot-out%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20haven't%20been%20seen%20at%20scale%20since%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%20According%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20F-22%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhushkit.net%2Ftag%2Ftyphoon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edecimated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20the%20Typhoon%20when%20able%20to%20engage%20from%20beyond%20visual%20range%20because%20it%20didn't%20have%20to%20fly%20with%20one%20wing%20tied%20behind%20its%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20real%20fight%2C%20the%20F-22%20would%20likely%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20Typhoon's%20presence%20well%20before%20the%20Typhoon%20was%20aware%20of%20it%2C%20and%20even%20if%20the%20Eurofighter%20and%20pilot%20proved%20too%20quick%20on%20the%20stick%20to%20be%20taken%20out%20with%20an%20AMRAAM%20at%20long%20distance%2C%20the%20Raptor%20could%20use%20its%20superior%20situational%20awareness%20and%20low%20observability%20to%20close%20in%20on%20its%20European%20foe%20from%20an%20advantageous%20position%2C%20greatly%20improving%20its%20chances%20of%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20perhaps%20most%20importantly%20of%20all%2C%20Raptor%20fans%20will%20argue%20that%20Germany%20was%20bragging%20about%20scoring%20a%20few%20kills%20against%20the%20Raptor%E2%80%A6%20but%20they%20never%20once%20claimed%20that%20the%20Eurofighter%20won%20more%20sparring%20matches%20than%20the%20Raptor%20did.%20They%20simply%20claimed%20that%20it%20won%20some%2C%20and%20that%20was%20with%20a%20number%20of%20distinct%20advantages%20handed%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20the%20headline-grabbing%20story%20wasn't%20about%20Eurofighters%20dominating%20the%20F-22%E2%80%A6%20It%20was%20about%20two%20of%20them%20managing%20to%20score%20wins%20at%20all%20against%20an%20aircraft%20many%20think%20of%20as%20invincible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22181bc1fa-45f8-4010-839e-1a18208615d5%5C%22%3EThe%20Typhoon-fan%20argument%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NATO%20Secretary%20General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%20sits%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20Eurofighter%20as%20it%20taxis%20back%20into%20the%20hangar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643cf649686a6f37bffe20c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENATO%20Secretary%20General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%20sits%20in%20the%20cockpit%20of%20a%20Eurofighter%20as%20it%20taxis%20back%20into%20the%20hangar%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Tactical%20Air%20Wing%2073%20%26quot%3BSteinhoff.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EBernd%20W%C3%BCstneck%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20in%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon's%20camp%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20argue%20that%20these%20exercises%2C%20like%20real%20combat%2C%20aren't%20about%20being%20fair.%20The%20Eurofighter's%20ability%20to%20stand%20and%20scrap%20with%20the%20Raptor%20in%20close%20quarters%20is%20proof%20positive%20that%20the%20Typhoon%20is%20capable%20of%20competing%20with%20the%20most%20advanced%20(and%20expensive)%20fighters%20on%20the%20planet%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20close-quarters%20air%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%2C%20combined%20with%20its%20improved%20avionics%20and%20beyond-visual%20range%20capabilities%20that%20have%20manifested%20since%20that%20interaction%2C%20make%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Fblog%2Freboot%2Feurofighter-typhoon-best-bang-your-buck-fighter-190018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebest%20pound-for-pound%20fighters%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20anywhere%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20foreign-sales%20price%20is%2C%20after%20all%2C%20right%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aerotime.aero%2Farticles%2F27553-Top-10-most-expensive-fighter-jets-in-2021%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEurofighter%2520Typhoon%253A%2520around%2520%2524124%2520million%26amp%3Btext%3DAnother%2520European%2520fighter%2520jet%252C%2520the%2Cexport%2520price%2520is%2520much%2520higher.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Earound%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24124%20million%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20an%20incredible%20bargain%20compared%20to%20the%20estimated%20%24400%20million%20or%20so%20per%20Raptor%2C%20at%20least%2C%20when%20you%20include%20its%20research%20and%20development%20costs%20in%20each%20F-22's%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Raptors%20did%20score%20more%20kills%20against%20Typhoons%20than%20the%20Germans%20did%20against%20Raptors%20as%20a%20number%20of%20sources%20have%20reported%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%204th%20generation%20Eurofighter%20was%20a%20genuine%20threat%20to%20the%20F-22%20at%20all%20proves%20that%20its%20supremacy%20isn't%20as%20assured%20as%20so%20many%20Raptor%20fanboys%20like%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6f1cdb5-3329-40b6-a04d-88b244d32095%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20truth%20is%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20these%20arguments%20are%20right.%20The%20F-22%20Raptor%20isn't%20considered%20the%20most%20dominant%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20in%20the%20sky%20because%20it%20can't%20lose.%20That's%20not%20how%20combat%20works%20%E2%80%94%20heck%2C%20it's%20not%20how%20any%20kind%20of%20fighting%20works.%20No%20matter%20how%20capable%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20advanced%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20well%20trained%2C%20anyone%20can%20find%20themselves%20knee-deep%20in%20a%20disadvantage%20they%20can't%20overcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Wicklund%2C%20a%20former%20Operations%20Specialist%20in%20the%20US%20Navy%2C%20made%20this%20point%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationgeekclub.com%2Fformer-us-navy-operations-specialist-explains-why-although-there-are-many-threats-that-could-potentially-shoot-down-the-f-22-the-raptor-is-still-the-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erather%20eloquently%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorld%20War%20II%20ace%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationgeekclub.com%2Ffinal-dogfight-may-8-1945-who-scored-the-last-aerial-victory-of-the-air-war-in-europe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EErich%20Hartmann%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20highest%20scoring%20ace%2C%20ever%2C%20with%20352%20kills.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20he%20never%20lost.%20He%20got%20shot%20down%2016%20times!%20He's%20still%20the%20greatest%20ace%2C%20because%20he%20won%20much%20more%20often%20than%20he%20lost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-22's%20advanced%20avionics%2C%20high%20degree%20of%20maneuverability%2C%20and%20extremely%20low%20observability%20all%20make%20it%20an%20incredibly%20capable%20platform%2C%20but%20nothing%20makes%20a%20fighter%20invincible.%20If%20you%20stack%20the%20deck%20against%20anything%2C%20it'll%20find%20its%20limits%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20finding%20those%20limits%2C%20of%20both%20the%20pilot%20and%20the%20platform%2C%20is%20the%20real%20reason%20these%20exercises%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERed%20Flag%20isn't%20about%20winning%20internet%20dog%20fights%2C%20it's%20about%20going%20on%20to%20win%20real%20ones.%20Taking%20home%20a%20few%20W's%20in%20a%20series%20of%20staged%20exercises%20doesn't%20mean%20nothing%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20everything%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20German%20air%20force%20Tech.%20Sgt.%20awaits%20clearance%20to%20launch%20a%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20while%20a%20KC-135%20Stratotanker%20takes%20off%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643d0eaf27898f532d7a33e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerman%20air%20force%20Tech.%20Sgt.%20Alex%20Muller%20awaits%20clearance%20to%20launch%20a%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20while%20a%20KC-135%20Stratotanker%20takes%20off%20during%20Red%20Flag%20Alaska.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Tech.%20Sgt.%20Michael%20Holzworth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%2C%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20is%20an%20incredibly%20capable%204th%20generation%20fighter%2C%20but%20when%20you%20pit%20it%20against%20a%205th%20generation%20fighter%2C%20that%20stealthy%20opponent%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20F-22%2C%20F-35%2C%20or%20maybe%20even%20J-20%20%E2%80%94%20is%20likely%20going%20to%20win%20most%20engagements%20in%20a%20relatively%20boring%20(and%20rather%20sneaky)%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20these%20stealth%20jets%20happen%20to%20find%20themselves%20within%20gun's%20reach%20of%20the%20Eurofighter%2C%20the%20victor%20isn't%20as%20easy%20to%20divine.%20And%20that's%20an%20important%20lesson%20for%20both%204th%20and%205th%20generation%20pilots%20to%20take%20away%20from%20these%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20assertion%20is%20substantiated%20in%20numbers%20we%20can%20confirm%3A%20in%20its%20earliest%20appearances%20at%20Red%20Flag%20back%20in%202006%20and%202007%2C%20F-22s%20racked%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightglobal.com%2Fexport-ready-the-f-22%2F74029.article%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E144%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Farticle%2F0207raptor%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520F%252D22%2527s%2520team%2520blitzed%2Ccame%2520through%2520the%2520engagements%2520untouched.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E241%20wins%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20respectively%2C%20but%20lost%20a%20handful%20of%20jets%20as%20well%20to%20lowly%204th%20generation%20fighters%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.19fortyfive.com%2F2021%2F11%2Fhow-an-old-f-16-killed-a-stealth-f-22-raptor-in-a-dogfight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elike%20the%20F-16C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20the%20first%20platform%20ever%20to%20down%20an%20F-22.%20in%20a%20mock%20dogfight.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20F-22's%20first%20air-to-air%20outing%20(without%20being%20limited%20to%20within%20visual%20range)%2C%20it%20took%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaviationist.com%2F2014%2F09%2F30%2Fthese-may-be-the-only-f-22s-achilles-heels-in-a-dogfight-against-4th-gen-fighter-jets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeight%20F-15s%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20them%20ever%20managing%20to%20paint%20it%20with%20a%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%E2%80%A6%20if%20you%20can%20get%20in%20close%20with%20the%20F-22%20and%20eliminate%20its%20technological%20advantages%2C%20the%20Raptor%20is%20just%20another%20aircraft%20in%20a%20fight%20for%20its%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Raptor's%20unique%20capabilities%20are%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20get%20to%20the%20merge%2C%20which%20is%20%5Badmittedly%5D%20only%20a%20very%20small%20spectrum%20of%20air%20combat%2C%20the%20Typhoon%20doesn't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20fear%20the%20F-22%20in%20all%20aspects.%20We%20gain%20energy%20better%20than%20the%20F-22%20when%20we%20are%20slow%2C%20for%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20Fighter%20Wing%2074%20commander%C2%A0Col.%20Andreas%20Pfeiffer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdefenseissues.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F10%2F20%2Fcleaning-up-red-flag-alaska-f-22-vs-typhoon-debate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20mock%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20all%20reminds%20me%20of%20something%20an%20American%20intelligence%20contractor%20told%20me%20years%20ago%20about%20US%20special%20operations%20units.%20They're%20the%20most%20elite%20operators%20in%20the%20world%20with%20the%20best%20training%2C%20the%20best%20equipment%2C%20and%20the%20best%20support%E2%80%A6%20but%20just%20about%20every%20Navy%20SEAL%2C%20Delta%20operator%2C%20or%20Army%20Ranger%20who's%20been%20killed%20in%20combat%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20wasn't%20taken%20down%20by%20a%20similarly%20elite%20group%20of%20ISIS%20or%20Al-Qaeda%20commandos.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it's%20a%20poorly%20trained%20young%20man%20with%20a%20poorly%20maintained%20AK-47%2C%20no%20body%20armor%2C%20and%20some%20luck%20on%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20give%20your%20warfighters%20all%20the%20advantages%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20nobody%20knows%20how%20a%20fight%20will%20play%20out%20until%20it%20does.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Farticle%2F0207raptor%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520F%252D22%2527s%2520team%2520blitzed%2Ccame%2520through%2520the%2520engagements%2520untouched.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Air%20Force%20Col.%20Thomas%20Bergeson%2C%20in%20Red%20Flag%20exercises%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20a%20great%20day%20if%20you%20lose%20only%2010%25%20of%20your%20forces.%26quot%3B%20And%20he's%20not%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-22%20raptor%20f%2022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F570e62aa9105841c008bc582%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20F-22%20Raptors%20fly%20over%20Alaska.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20numbers%20where%20you%20never%20have%20a%20loss%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20you're%20training%20to%20your%20full%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Lt.%20Col.%20Wade%20Tolliver%2C%2027th%20FS%20commander%2C%20back%20in%202007.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20have%20that%20simulated%20loss%2C%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20push%20ourselves%20to%20be%20as%20capable%20as%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20unfortunate%20reality%20of%20defense%20technology%20analysis.%20The%20real%20answer%20is%20rarely%20pithy%2C%20rarely%20simple%2C%20and%20rarely%20can%20stand%20on%20its%20own%20without%20some%20broader%20context.%20The%20internet%20prefers%20that%20we%20speak%20in%20concise%20absolutes%2C%20but%20the%20only%20incisive%20answer%20you%20can%20really%20give%20when%20asked%20which%20out%20of%20the%20two%20contemporary%20platforms%20is%20best%20is%E2%80%A6%20it%20depends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20mission%2C%20the%20circumstances%2C%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement%2C%20the%20pilots%2C%20the%20mission%20planning%2C%20the%20training%2C%20the%20budget%2C%20the%20over-arching%20combat%20doctrine%2C%20and%20if%20any%20of%20the%20pilots%20had%20two%20extra%20cups%20of%20coffee%20this%20morning%20and%20is%20distracted%20by%20the%20pressing%20need%20to%20find%20a%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20magical%20the%20F-22%2C%20any