20support%20for%203D%20sound%20formats%20like%20Dolby%20Atmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20good%20luck%20getting%20anywhere%20near%20a%20similar%20setup%20at%20this%20price%20elsewhere.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20dip%20your%20toes%20into%20surround%20sound%20at%20a%20serious%20bargain%2C%20this%20is%20the%20best%20soundbar%20with%20a%20subwoofer%20for%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-budget-soundbars%5C%22%3Ebest%20budget%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20soundbars%20with%20subwoofers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20V%20Series%205.1%20soundbar%20on%20a%20TV%20stand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6607159a3f923f7dab02c926%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20put%20each%20soundbar%20we%20evaluate%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20soundbars%20with%20subwoofers%2C%20we%20tested%20multiple%20models%20for%20hours%20on%20end%20across%20various%20sources.%20Sound%20quality%20is%20our%20top%20priority%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20emphasis%20on%20potent%20and%20foundational%20bass.%20We%20also%20consider%20other%20factors%2C%20including%20supported%20audio%20formats%2C%20how%20easy%20each%20soundbar%20is%20to%20set%20up%20and%20use%2C%20and%20support%20for%20advanced%20features%20like%20WiFi%20streaming%2C%20smart%20assistants%2C%20and%20multiple%20HDMI%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20assess%20each%20soundbar's%20design%2C%20considering%20its%20aesthetic%20qualities%20and%20how%20well%20it%20fits%20into%20the%20average%20TV%20room.%20We%20then%20spend%20multiple%20days%20with%20each%20bar%20we%20evaluate%2C%20putting%20them%20through%20various%20tests%20with%20familiar%20material%2C%20from%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20to%20specific%20music%20playlists.%20We%20test%20a%20variety%20of%20sound%20sources%2C%20from%20streaming%20services%20to%20physical%20media%2C%20as%20well%20as%20listening%20to%20both%20compressed%20and%20lossless%20audio%20via%20apps%20like%20Spotify%20and%20Amazon%20Music.%20We%20also%20use%20each%20bar%20for%20regular%20daily%20listening%2C%20striving%20to%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20how%20it%20is%20to%20own%20it%20from%20a%20buyer's%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20testing%20sound%20quality%2C%20we%20look%20at%20many%20elements%2C%20from%20dynamics%20and%20dialogue%20clarity%20to%20tonal%20balance%20across%20the%20treble%2C%20midrange%2C%20and%20bass%20registers.%20To%20find%20the%20best%20soundbar%20with%20subwoofer%20combos%20in%20particular%2C%20we're%20looking%20for%20smooth%2C%20accurate%2C%20and%20musical%20bass%2C%20as%20well%20as%20good%20balance%20and%20fluidity%20between%20the%20subwoofer%20and%20soundbar.%20Any%20obvious%20difference%20between%20the%20tonal%20color%20of%20the%20subwoofer%20and%20the%20bar%20is%20grounds%20for%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20we%20test%20parameters%20like%20WiFi%20and%20Bluetooth%20reliability%2C%20navigation%20of%20connected%20apps%20and%20settings%2C%20and%20the%20responsiveness%20and%20accuracy%20of%20smart%20assistants%2C%20where%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20soundbar%20with%20a%20subwoofer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20HW-Q990C%20soundbar%20underside%2C%20showing%20the%20input%20section.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ea8cf6561dd877e7c6252%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20soundbars%20have%20HDMI%20ARC%20or%20eARC%20ports%20to%20easily%20connect%20to%20modern%20TVs.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20established%20that%20you%20want%20a%20soundbar%20with%20a%20subwoofer%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20primary%20things%20to%20target%20as%20you%20hone%20your%20search.%20First%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20check%20for%20good%20connectivity%20options.%20Every%20modern%20soundbar%20should%20have%20HDMI%20ARC%20or%20eARC%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20simple%20to%20connect%20to%20an%20HDMI%20ARC-compatible%20TV%20and%20use%20its%20remote%20to%20control%20power%20and%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20sold%20today%20have%20this%20feature%2C%20but%20if%20your%20TV%20doesn't%20have%20HDMI%20ARC%20or%20eARC%20(it%20should%20be%20labeled%20in%20the%20inputs%20cubby)%2C%20you%20can%20often%20use%20an%20optical%20connection%20as%20an%20alternative.%20However%2C%20HDMI%20ARC%20is%20required%20to%20play%20Dolby%20Atmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirtually%20every%20modern%20soundbar%20includes%20Bluetooth%20support%2C%20but%20higher-quality%20systems%20also%20have%20WiFi%20for%20over-the-air%20updates%20and%20better%20streaming%20quality.%20Features%20like%20AirPlay%202%20for%20iPhones%2C%20Chromecast%20for%20Android%20devices%2C%20and%20Spotify%20Connect%20are%20also%20relatively%20standard%2C%20making%20it%20handy%20to%20stream%20songs%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-music-streaming-service-subscription%5C%22%3Ebest%20music%20services%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20more%20options%20your%20bar%20supports%2C%20the%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoundbars%20with%20WiFi%20support%20may%20also%20offer%20built-in%20voice%20assistants%20like%20Alexa%20or%20Google%20Assistant.%20If%20you're%20interested%20in%20using%20your%20soundbar%20as%20a%20smart%20home%20hub%20or%20controller%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20bar%20has%20built-in%20microphones%20for%20voice%20commands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20soundbar%20subwoofer%20combo%2C%20you'll%20be%20looking%20at%20a%202.1-channel%20configuration%20at%20the%20low%20end%2C%20while%20advanced%20systems%20with%20Dolby%20Atmos%20will%20generally%20offer%20multi-channel%20configurations%20like%205.1.2.%20The%20first%20number%20in%20the%20series%20represents%20the%20front-facing%20channels%20in%20the%20soundbar%2C%20the%20middle%20number%20represents%20the%20subwoofer%20(bass)%20channel%2C%20and%20the%20last%20number%20defines%20how%20many%20height%20or%20upfiring%20channels%20the%20bar%20supports%20(if%20any)%20for%20Dolby%20Atmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20you'll%20usually%20pay%20a%20premium%20to%20get%20a%20soundbar%20that%20supports%20it%20or%20its%20primary%20rival%20DTS%3AX.%20Sometimes%20called%203D%2C%20spatial%2C%20or%20object-based%20audio%2C%20these%20advanced%20formats%20include%20traditional%20surround%20sound%20channels%20on%20the%20horizontal%20plane%2C%20as%20well%20as%20height%20channels%20to%20add%20a%20vertical%20element%20that%20creates%20a%20deeper%20sense%20of%20immersion.%20Check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%3EDolby%20Atmos%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EFAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221759%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Vizio%20V-Seres%20subwoofer%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20a%20carpeted%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643bbccf27898f532d792c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20the%20best%20bass%20performance%2C%20there's%20no%20substitute%20for%20a%20dedicated%20subwoofer.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20do%20I%20need%20a%20subwoofer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20answer%20is%20physics.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20producing%20true%2C%20authoritative%20bass%2C%20advanced%20acoustics%20and%20digital%20processing%20are%20no%20match%20for%20bigger%20speaker%20drivers.%20The%20larger%20drivers%20inside%20dedicated%20subwoofers%20can%20physically%20move%20more%20air%20than%20smaller%20speakers%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20properly%20recreate%20the%20low-frequency%20waveforms%20that%20eventually%20make%20their%20way%20to%20our%20ears%20with%20authenticity%20and%20accuracy.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20powerful%20explosions%2C%20floor-rattling%20thunder%2C%20and%20rich%2C%20low%20musical%20performance%2C%20a%20subwoofer%20is%20all%20but%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20add%20a%20subwoofer%20to%20a%20soundbar%20later%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20soundbars%20offer%20the%20option%20to%20add%20a%20subwoofer%20or%20surround%20sound%20speakers%20after%20the%20fact.%20These%20are%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bmodular%26quot%3B%20systems%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20purchase%20extra%20components%20later.%20Some%20soundbars%2C%20including%20options%20from%20Klipsch%20and%20Sennheiser%2C%20even%20have%20a%20standard%20subwoofer%20output%2C%20letting%20you%20connect%20a%20traditional%20subwoofer%20from%20any%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20many%20companies%20charge%20a%20major%20premium%20for%20soundbar%20models%20that%20use%20modular%20designs.%20Adding%20a%20subwoofer%20made%20by%20a%20different%20brand%20may%20also%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20balance%20the%20two%20components%20tonally.%20If%20bass%20is%20an%20important%20factor%20for%20you%2C%20we%20recommend%20buying%20a%20soundbar%20and%20subwoofer%20combo%20from%20the%20start%20to%20get%20the%20best%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20size%20soundbar%20and%20subwoofer%20should%20I%20get%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESize%20is%20always%20a%20determining%20factor%20when%20purchasing%20a%20soundbar.%20The%20first%20thing%20to%20consider%20is%20whether%20your%20entertainment%20console%20is%20long%20enough%20to%20support%20your%20soundbar%20of%20choice.%20Many%20soundbars%20range%20from%2036%20to%2046%20inches%20or%20longer%2C%20especially%20for%20high-performance%20bars%20with%20many%20drivers%2C%20such%20as%20those%20that%20support%20Dolby%20Atmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20want%20to%20ensure%20your%20soundbar%20won't%20block%20your%20TV%20screen%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20TV%20sits%20on%20a%20stand%20rather%20than%20being%20mounted%20on%20a%20wall.%20Most%20soundbars%20are%20designed%20to%20sit%20around%20three%20inches%20tall%20or%20less%2C%20but%20you'll%20want%20to%20do%20some%20measurements%20so%20you%20don't%20run%20into%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20soundbars%20on%20this%20list%2C%20you'll%20also%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you've%20got%20space%20for%20your%20subwoofer.%20Subwoofers%20can%20range%20from%20tall%20and%20skinny%20to%20short%20and%20stout%2C%20so%20again%2C%20do%20some%20measurements%20to%20ensure%20you've%20got%20good%20placement%20options.%20Most%20setups%20work%20well%20with%20the%20subwoofer%20placed%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20the%20left%20or%20right%20of%20the%20TV%20console%2C%20but%20it's%20best%20to%20have%20some%20room%20to%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20add%20a%20soundbar%20with%20surround%20sound%20(or%20satellite)%20speakers%2C%20make%20sure%20you've%20got%20stands%20or%20shelves%20that%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20properly%20place%20the%20speakers%20slightly%20behind%20and%20to%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20main%20listening%20position.%20Dolby%20offers%20some%20helpful%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dolby.com%2Fabout%2Fsupport%2Fguide%2Fsurround-sound-speaker-setup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeaker%20configuration%20guides%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20this%20purpose.%20You'll%20also%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you've%20got%20power%20outlets%20in%20reach%20for%20wireless%20surround%20speakers%20or%20long%20enough%20cables%20to%20plug%20in%20wired%20options%20comfortably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbars-with-subwoofers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715719530000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643a64d9686a6f37bffc5e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbars-with-subwoofers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20get%20the%20best%20bass%20performance%20from%20a%20soundbar%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20model%20that%20includes%20a%20separate%20subwoofer.%20Check%20out%20our%20top%20picks%20for%20various%20budgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ryan%20Waniata)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbars-with-subwoofers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bruce%20Springsteen%20Documentary%20About%20E%20Street%20Band%20World%20Tour%20Set%20at%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715719419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fimage002-1.png%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D427%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236003198%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu%20have%20set%20a%20new%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20documentary%20for%20an%20October%20premiere.%20%E2%80%9CRoad%20Diary%3A%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20and%20The%20E%20Street%20Band%E2%80%9D%20will%20follow%20the%20band%E2%80%99s%202023-2024%20world%20tour%2C%20featuring%20footage%20from%20band%20rehearsals%20and%20backstage%20moments%2C%20conversations%20with%20Springsteen%20as%20he%20develops%20the%20setlist%20and%20archival%20clips%20of%20the%20E%20Street%20Band.%20The%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Se