0tech%20innovations.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20bolstering%20its%205G%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnne%20Neuberger%2C%20the%20deputy%20national%20security%20advisor%20for%20cyber%20and%20emerging%20tech%2C%20said%20that%205G%20and%206G%20were%20some%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20strategic%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20since%20telecom%20and%20data-center%20infrastructure%20houses%20the%20data%20required%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-secure-5g-networks-combat-cyber-threats-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20artificial-intelligence%20models%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20at%20the%20annual%20RSA%20Conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20she%20spoke%20at%20a%20fireside%20chat%20on%20cybersecurity%20and%20new%20technologies%20like%205G%20and%20AI%2C%20which%20was%20moderated%20by%20Niloofar%20Razi%20Howe%2C%20an%20operating%20partner%20at%20Capitol%20Meridian%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuberger%20discussed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20telecom%20sector%2C%20saying%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20the%20US%20was%20its%20lack%20of%20competitive%20technology%20in%20telecom%20infrastructure.%20She%20said%20the%20US%20needed%20to%20improve%20its%20hardware%20and%20encourage%20competition%20among%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20especially%20important%2C%20Neuberger%20said%2C%20as%20the%20US%20is%20engaged%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-government-approves-more-ai-models-rivals-us-report-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20arms%20race%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20China%20and%20Chinese%20telecom%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-is-firing-back-again-in-china-chip-semiconductor-wars-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuawei%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20Chinese%20technology%20gets%20more%20embedded%20in%20the%20technology%20Americans%20use%20daily%2C%20whether%20it's%205G%20technology%20or%20connected%20vehicles%2C%20the%20US%20needs%20to%20consider%20national%20security%20risks%20in%20how%20data%20is%20collected%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20the%20point%20we%20can%20say%2C%20what's%20a%20thoughtful%20approach%20that%20protects%20Americans'%20sensitive%20data%2C%20that%20protects%20Americans'%20navigation%20data%20while%20also%20promoting%20innovation%3F%26quot%3B%20Neuberger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20telecommunications%20industry%20affects%20valuable%20information%20belonging%20to%20American%20companies%20and%20the%20government.%20It's%20also%20often%20managed%20and%20updated%20remotely%2C%20so%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20secure%2C%20Neuberger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTelecom%20systems%20are%20so%20complex%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20have%20confidence%20in%20those%20vendors%2C%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20trust%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuberger%20highlighted%20some%20of%20the%20government%20initiatives%20for%20investing%20in%205G%2C%20including%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20%241.5%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntia.gov%2Fprogram%2Finnovation-fund%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPublic%20Wireless%20Supply%20Chain%20Innovation%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20bring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nist.gov%2Fopen-radio-access-network-open-ran%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20telecommunications%20and%20advance%20innovation%20in%20the%20wireless%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20been%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20bring%20in%20innovation%20to%20bring%20in%20new%20players%20to%20allow%20our%20traditional%20strength%20in%20software%20to%20come%20to%20bear%2C%26quot%3B%20Neuberger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrants%20from%20these%20these%20types%20of%20funds%20have%20helped%20US%20allies.%20They%20have%20allowed%20global%20telecom%20companies%2C%20including%20those%20from%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Europe%2C%20to%20test%20new%20technology%20together%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%20The%20US%20has%20also%20been%20building%20a%20telecom%20partnership%20with%20India%2C%20as%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20telecom%20markets%20in%20the%20world%2C%20along%20with%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20White%20House%20launched%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNational-Spectrum-Strategy.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Spectrum%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20promote%20innovation%20in%20wireless%20technologies.%20Neuberger%20said%20this%20included%20industries%20such%20as%20connected%20vehicles%20and%20defense%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20technologies%20allowed%20the%20US%20to%20aid%20Ukraine%20when%20Russia%20struck%20down%20its%20electric%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20think%20about%20how%20we%20lead%20in%20these%20connected%20industries%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20have%20to%20think%20about%20creative%20ways%20to%20use%20spectrum%20more%20efficiently%20and%20differently%2C%26quot%3B%20Neuberger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frsa-conference-us-national-security-5g-infrastructure-ai-anne-neuberger-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715718325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664284a7f27898f532d74292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frsa-conference-us-national-security-5g-infrastructure-ai-anne-neuberger-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anne%20Neuberger%2C%20the%20d