C%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reach%2016%20points%20and%20thus%20complicating%20things%20for%20the%20three%20sides.%20But%20now%20they%20can%20reach%20a%20maximum%20of%2014%20points.%20Now%20LSG%20and%20DC%20have%20very%20faint%20chance%20of%20advancing%20because%20of%20their%20poor%20run-rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%20-%C2%A014%20points%20in%2013%20matches%20(NRR%20%2B0.528)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatches%20remaining%20-%201%20(vs%20RCB)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108591-ruturaj-gaikwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20have%20a%20good%20chance.%20The%20have%2014%20points%20in%2013%20matches%20(NRR%20%2B0.528).%20If%20they%20beat%20RCB%2C%20they%20are%20through.%20A%20loss%20against%20RCB%20in%20the%20final%20league%20game%20won't%20knock%20the%20defending%20champions%20out%20either.%20They%20would%20then%20hope%20that%20RCB%20do%20not%20surpass%20them%20on%20NRR.%C2%A0If%20LSG%20win%20their%20last%20game%20(and%20reach%2014)%2C%20CSK%20will%20still%20be%20favourites%20to%20go%20through%20due%20to%20a%20much%20superior%20NRR.%C2%A0They%20would%20also%20hope%20SRH%20(14%20from%2012%20games)%20lose%20both%20their%20matches%2C%20so%20that%20they%20have%20it%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunrisers%20Hyderabad%20-%2014%20points%20in%2012%20matches%20(NRR%20%2B0.406)%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatches%20remaining%20-%202%20(vs%20GT%20and%20PBKS)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWins%20in%20the%20remaining%20two%20matches%20will%20guarantee%20a%20playoff%20spot%20for%20SRH.%20Even%20if%20they%20lose%20one%20of%20their%20matches%2C%20they%20will%20still%20go%20through.%20If%20they%20lose%20both%20their%20game%2C%20then%20it%20will%20all%20come%20down%20to%20net%20run-rate.%20If%20SRH%20lose%20both%20of%20their%20remaining%20matches%20while%20LSG%20and%20RCB%20win%20their%20last%20games%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20side%20will%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20the%20NRR%20to%20be%20in%20the%20top%204.%20If%20CSK%20beat%20RCB%2C%20and%20SRH%20lose%20both%20their%20games%2C%20they%20will%20hope%20to%20keep%20better%20run-rate%20than%20LSG%20and%20DC%20to%20grab%20that%20last%20play-off%20spots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESRH%20could%20still%20finish%20above%20RR%20if%20the%20side%20win%20their%20two%20fixtures%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20drop%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnuktb9d8_points-table_625x300_14_May_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20-%2012%20points%20from%2013%20games%20(NRR%20%2B0.387)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatches%20remaining%20-%201%20(vs%20CSK)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20five-match%20winning%20streak%2C%20RCB%20have%20had%20a%20massive%20turnaround.%20They%20won%20only%20one%20out%20of%20their%20first%20seven%20games%20but%20since%20then%20it's%20a%20different%20side%20altogether.%20For%20RCB%20to%20qualify%2C%20they%20have%20to%20beat%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20to%20reach%2014%20points.%20They%20would%20then%20hope%20that%20their%20NRR%20is%20above%20the%20other%20sides%20vying%20for%20the%20fourth%20spot%20in%20the%20playoffs.%20They%20would%20also%20hope%20SRH%20to%20lose%20both%20their%20remaining%20games%20or%20LSG%20don't%20win%20their%20last%20match%20by%20a%20big%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%20Capitals%20-%2014%20points%20from%2014%20matches%20(NRR%20-0.377)%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatches%20remaining%20-%200%3C%2Fp%3E%5C