%20for%20her%20-%20an%20unique%20and%20poignant%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20a%20groom%20for%20somebody%20who%20died%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20parents%20got%20an%20advertisement%20published%20in%20a%20widely%20read%20newspaper%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advertisement%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BSeeking%20groom%20who%20passed%2030%20years%20ago%20for%20a%20bride%20(sic)%20who%20passed%2030%20years%20ago.%20Please%20call%20the%20number%20to%20arrange%20a%20Pretha%20Maduve%20(marriage%20of%20spirits).%26quot%3B%20Despite%20exhaustive%20efforts%20by%20relatives%20and%20friends%2C%20finding%20a%20suitable%20dead%20groom%20of%20the%20same%20age%20and%20caste%20proved%20elusive%2C%20say%20the%20heartbroken%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unconventional%20practice%20underscores%20a%20longstanding%20tradition%20in%20Tulunadu%20-%20the%20region%20spread%20across%20three%20coastal%20districts%20of%20Karnataka%20and%20portion%20of%20neighbouring%20Kasargod%20district%20in%20Kerala%20where%20local%20dialect%20Tulu%20is%20spoken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20region%2C%20arranging%20marriages%20for%20dead%20individuals%20holds%20deep%20emotional%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tuluva%20folklore%20experts%2C%20the%20departed%20remain%20connected%20to%20their%20families%2C%20sharing%20in%20their%20joys%20and%20sorrows.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20rituals%20like%20'Vaikunta%20Samaradhane'%20and%20'Pinda%20Pradana'%20are%20eschewed%20in%20favour%20of%20offerings%20of%20food%20and%20the%20arrangement%20of%20marriages%20for%20departed%20souls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715709240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fellf7tio_indian-wedding-generic_625x300_24_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3