hared%20with%20Norwegian%20financial%20outlet%20E24%20and%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20which%20coordinated%20an%20investigative%20project%20with%20media%20outlets%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20Titled%20%E2%80%98Dubai%20Unlocked'%2C%20the%20collaboration%20includes%2074%20partners%20from%2058%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20reported%20that%20the%20details%20of%20%E2%80%9Can%20astounding%20volume%20of%20leaked%20property%20data%20that%20includes%20over%2017%2C000%20properties%20listed%20as%20belonging%20to%20Pakistani%20nationals%20up%20to%20the%20spring%20of%202022%E2%80%9D%20were%20known%20to%20journalists%20from%20scores%20of%20media%20outlets%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20while%2017%2C000%20Pakistani%20citizens%20are%20listed%20owners%20in%20the%202022%20leak%2C%20academics%20using%20the%20data%20and%20additional%20sources%20put%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20Pakistani%20owners%20of%20residential%20property%20in%20Dubai%20at%2022%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20further%20estimate%20that%20the%20apartments%20and%20villas%20may%20have%20been%20worth%20more%20than%20USD%2010%20billion%20at%20the%20start%20of%202022%2C%20but%20with%20the%20more%20than%2025%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20property%20prices%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20real%20worth%20of%20Pakistanis'%20residential%20properties%20in%20Dubai%20could%20now%20be%20well%20above%20USD%2012.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20the%20data%20you%20are%20talking%20about%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20information%20on%20residence%20status%2C%20we%20will%20make%20sure%20those%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20pay%20tax%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20rental%20income%20or%20capital%20value%20are%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Malik%20Amjed%20Zubair%20Tiwana%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Federal%20Board%20of%20Revenue%20(FBR)%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20news%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20a%20sensitive%20matter%2C%20and%20perhaps%20the%20law%20will%20have%20to%20change%2C%20but%20with%20political%20will%20we%20will%20go%20all%20out%20against%20tax%20evaders.%20The%20government%20is%20prepared%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bcitizenship%20has%20no%20importance%20in%20tax%20law%26quot%3B%20as%20taxation%20is%20linked%20to%20residence%20status.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20information%20from%20the%20immigration%20department%20of%20Dubai%20to%20determine%20tax%20status%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20materialised.%26quot%3B%20Ali%20Rahim%2C%20tax%20lawyer%20and%20former%20Karachi%20Tax%20Bar%20Association%20president%2C%20said%20that%20the%20entire%20world%20income%20of%20resident%20Pakistanis%20is%20liable%20to%20be%20taxed%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20they%20can%20get%20credit%20against%20their%20total%20tax%20payment%20for%20any%20taxes%20paid%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani%20residents%20(those%20in%20the%20country%20for%20more%20than%20183%20days%20per%20year)%20with%20assets%20abroad%20have%20to%20value%20them%20at%20the%20current%20exchange%20rate%20and%20pay%20one%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20that%20if%20the%20value%20of%20the%20asset%20is%20more%20than%20Rs%20100%20million.%20This%20law%20is%20being%20challenged%20in%20the%20high%20courts%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-resident%20or%20overseas%20Pakistanis%20are%20only%20liable%20to%20pay%20tax%20on%20income%20generated%20in%20Pakistan.%20They%20are%20not%20required%20to%20file%20a%20wealth%20statement%20or%20declare%20overseas%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDawn%20also%20clarified%20that%20a%20mere%20mention%20of%20someone%20in%20the%20data%20is%20not%20evidence%20in%20itself%20of%20financial%20crime%20or%20tax%20fraud.%20Nor%20does%20the%20data%20contain%20information%20such%20as%20residence%20status%2C%20sources%20of%20income%2C%20tax%20declarations%20of%20rental%20income%20or%20capital%20gains.%20In%20fact%2C%20several%20of%20those%20approached%20for%20comment%20on%20their%20properties%20said%20they%20were%20declared%20to%20the%20tax%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20does%20paint%20an%20astonishing%20picture%20of%20contrasts.%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20developing%20country%20teetering%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20economic%20collapse%2C%20begging%20international%20lenders%20and%20friendly%20countries%20for%20lifelines%20in%20single%20digit%20billions%2C%20features%20prominently%20in%20the%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20website.%20PTI%20SH%20ZH%20ZH%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715709120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2F5npl2qas_pakistan-flag-reuters_625x300_24_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistanis-own-properties-worth-12-5-billion-in-dubai-report-5663881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20cash-strapped%20Pakistan%20running%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20loan%2C%20its%20rich%20nationals%20own%20between%2017%2C000%20to%2022%2C000%20properties%20worth%20USD%2012.5%20billion%20in%20Dubai%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistanis-own-properties-worth-12-5-billion-in-dubai-report-5663881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistanis-own-properties-worth-12-5-billion-in-dubai-report-5663881%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpakistanis-own-properties-worth-12-5-billion-in-dubai-report-5663881%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20signs%20into%20law%20ban%20on%20Russian%20nuclear%20reactor%20fuel%20imports%22%2C%22conten