0stop%20in%20north-west%20London%20in%20Tuesday.%20He%20was%20sent%20into%20custody%20at%20a%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%20Mukhey%2C%20who%20worked%20part-time%20for%20the%20National%20Health%20Service%20(NHS)%20as%20a%20medical%20secretary%2C%20was%20waiting%20at%20the%20Burnt%20Oak%20Broadway%20bus%20stop%20in%20the%20Edgware%20area%20of%20London%20last%20week%20when%20Jalal%20Debella%20allegedly%20stabbed%20her%20in%20chest%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appeared%20at%20the%20Old%20Bailey%20Court%20in%20London%20and%20will%20enter%20his%20plea%20of%20guilty%20or%20not%20guilty%20at%20the%20next%20hearing%20in%20the%20case%20scheduled%20for%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20were%20called%20at%20around%2011%3A50hrs%20on%20Thursday%2C%209%20May%2C%20to%20reports%20of%20a%20stabbing%20in%20Burnt%20Oak%20Broadway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOfficers%2C%20London%20Ambulance%20Service%20(LAS)%20and%20London's%20Air%20Ambulance%20(HEMS)%20all%20attended%20the%20scene%2C%20where%20a%2066-year-old%20woman%20was%20treated%20for%20knife%20wounds.%20Sadly%2C%20despite%20the%20best%20efforts%20of%20emergency%20services%2C%20she%20died%20at%20the%20scene.%20Her%20family%20have%20been%20informed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalal%20Debella%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20murder%20in%20the%20Colindale%20area%20of%20north%20London%20later%20on%20May%209%20and%20charged%20with%20Anita%20Mukhey's%20murder%20and%20also%20for%20possession%20of%20an%20offensive%20weapon.%20The%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS)%20told%20the%20court%20that%20a%20preliminary%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20found%20to%20be%20sharp%20force%20injuries%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20chest%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnita%20Mukhey%2C%2066%20years%20old%2C%20was%20a%20married%20mother%20and%20grandmother%20devoted%20to%20her%20family%2C%20who%20also%20worked%20part-time%2