%20the%20alleged%20defrauding%20of%20a%2017-member%20lender%20bank%20consortium%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2034%2C000%20crore%2C%20officials%20said%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Wadhawan%2C%20arrested%20from%20Mumbai%20on%20Monday%20night%2C%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20special%20court%20here%20which%20remanded%20him%20in%20judicial%20custody%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20director%20of%20DHFL%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Kapil%2C%20were%20earlier%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20on%20July%2019%2C%202022%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20had%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%2075%20entities%20including%20Kapil%20and%20Dheeraj%20Wadhawan%20on%20October%2015%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20granted%20%26quot%3Bstatutory%26quot%3B%20bail%20from%20the%20special%20court%20on%20December%203%2C%202022%2C%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20investigation%20was%20incomplete%20and%20the%20charge%20sheet%20filed%20was%20piecemeal.%20This%20order%20was%20upheld%20by%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20challenged%20the%20order%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20set%20aside%20the%20bail%20orders%20noting%20that%20the%20Special%20Court%20as%20well%20as%20the%20High%20Court%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20serious%20error%20of%20law%26quot%3B%20in%20disregarding%20the%20legal%20position%20enunciated%20and%20settled%20by%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20Dheeraj%20Wadhawan%20got%20interim%20bail%20in%20a%20separate%20matter%20on%20medical%20grounds%20from%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20as%20he%20was%20admitted%20at%20the%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20for%20treatment.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20regularised%20the%20bail%20in%20that%20case%20on%20May%202%20this%20year%20and%20had%20also%20extended%20his%20protection%20from%20CBI%20arrest%20for%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20arrested%20Mr%20Wadhawan%20after%20the%20pr