umoon%2C%20alleging%20that%20Indian%20military%20helicopter%20pilots%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20carried%20out%20an%20unauthorised%20operation%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Maldives%20asserted%20that%20Indian%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20Maldives%20have%20always%20operated%20according%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20procedures%20and%20with%20due%20authorisation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clarification%20came%20days%20after%20India%20completed%20the%20withdrawal%20of%2076%20military%20personnel%20from%20the%20Maldives%20following%20a%20demand%20by%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu.%20Relations%20between%20India%20and%20Maldives%20deteriorated%20since%20Muizzu%2C%20a%20pro-China%20leader%2C%20came%20to%20power%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20had%20set%20May%2010%20as%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Indian%20military%20troops%20from%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20here%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Ghassan%20said%20he%20knew%20of%20one%20of%20the%20aviation%20platforms%20undertaking%20an%20unauthorised%20sortie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20narrated%20an%20incident%20where%20one%20of%20the%20two%20helicopters%20operated%20by%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20in%20the%20Maldives%20landed%20in%20Thimarafushi%2C%20allegedly%20without%20permission%20-%20a%20case%2C%20which%20he%20said%2C%20was%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Parliament's%20Committee%20on%20National%20Security%20Services%20(241%20Committee)%2C%20when%20he%20was%20a%20lawmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Indian%20mission%20dismissed%20the%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20Maldives%20have%20always%20operated%20as%20per%20agreed%20procedures%20and%20with%20due%20authorisation%20from%20the%20Maldives%20National%20Defence%20Force%20(MNDF)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20remarks%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20the%20High%20Commission%20said%20the%20particular%20incident%20which%20saw%20an%20emergency%20landing%20at%20Thimarafushi%20on%20October%209%2C%202019%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bnecessitated%20due%20to%20an%20unforeseen%20exigency.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20specific%20sortie%20on%2009%20October%202019%20referred%20to%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20was%20also%20undertaken%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20MNDF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emergency%20landing%20at%20Thimarafushi%20was%20necessitated%20due%20to%20an%20unforeseen%20exigency%2C%20which%20was%20carried%20out%20after%20taking%20necessary%20on-ground%20approvals%20from%20the%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20(ATC)%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20platform%20and%20crew%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Commission%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20local%20media%20reports%2C%20on%20May%2011%2C%20the%20MNDF%20revealed%20that%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20who%20were%20previously%20operating%20the%20helicopters%20gifted%20to%20the%20Maldives%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20made%20a%20trip%20on%20the%20helicopter%20without%20notifying%20the%20Maldivian%20military%20during%20the%20administration%20of%20former%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20at%20the%20same%20press%20conference%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Ghassan%20also%20confessed%20that%20the%20Maldives%20military%20still%20does%20not%20have%20pilots%20capable%20of%20operating%20three%20aircraft%20donated%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20were%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20aircraft%20gifted%20by%20India.%20The%20helicopters%20and%20the%20aircraft%20were%20used%20primarily%20for%20medical%20evacuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20batch%20o