n%20till%20June-end.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20Dravid%20is%20unlikely%20to%20seek%20or%20get%20an%20extension.%20The%20tenure%20of%20the%20next%20coach%20will%20runs%20till%20December%2031%2C%202027.%20It%20effectively%20means%20that%20the%20coach%20will%20remain%20till%20the%202027%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20enough%20speculation%20about%20India's%20new%20coach.%20An%20overseas%20coach%20also%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbcci-india-head-coach-stephen-fleming-csk-rahul-dravid-9328784%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BCCI%20top%20brass%20has%20already%20informally%20held%20discussion%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Fleming%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F187-stephen-fleming-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStephen%20Fleming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20The%20New%20Zealander%20has%20been%20the%20coach%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20understands%20the%20Indian%20players%20and%20conditions%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20However%2C%20also%20added%20that%20with%20the%20new%20coach%20requiring%20to%20be%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20for%2010%20months%20in%20a%20year%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20Fleming%20actually%20applies%20or%20not.%20The%20deadline%20for%20applying%20for%20the%20post%20is%20May%2027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttributing%20sources%2C%20the%20report%20claimed%20that%20since%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20will%20be%20going%20through%20a%20transition%20phase%2C%20with%20youngsters%20taking%20centre-stage%20and%20veterans%20gradually%20leaving%2C%20Fleming%20is%20a%20good%20candidate.%20But%20as%20of%20now%2C%20Fleming%20has%20not%20communicated%20anything%20to%20the%20CSK%20management%20regarding%20leadving%20the%20franchise%2C%20with%20which%20he%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20titles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20required%20%26quot%3Bqualifications%2C%20experience%2C%20knowledge%20and%20skills%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20top%20post%20are%20also%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20have%20played%20minimum%20of%2030%20Test%20Matches%20or%2050%20ODI's%3B%20or%20Head%20Coach%20of%20a%20full%20member%20Test%20Playing%20Nation%2C%20for%20a%20minimum%20period%20of%202%20years%3B%20or%20Head%20Coach%20of%20an%20Associate%20member%20%2FIPL%20Team%20or%20Equivalent%20International%20League%2FFirst%20Class%20Teams%2F%20National%20A%20teams%2C%20for%20a%20minimum%20period%20of%203%20years%3B%20or%20Should%20have%20BCCI%20Level%203%20Certification%20or%20equivalent%3B%20and%20Should%20be%20below%2060%20years%20of%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20release%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20remuneration%2C%20the%20BCCI%20says%20its%20%26quot%3Bnegotiable%20and%20will%20be%20commensurated%20with%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'operating%20environment'%20column%20is%20also%20interesting.%20It%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BMust%20be%20willing%20to%20meet%20work%20expectations%20and%20pressures%20associated%20with%20handling%20marquee%20athletes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715699760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fnledas5_indian-cricket-team_625x300_30_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fnot-gautam-gambhir-or-justin-langer-bcci-already-in-talks-with-this-ipl-coach-to-take-charge-of-india-report-5663249%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20tenure%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20ends%20with%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20which%20will%20run%20till%20June-end%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricketer%20To%20Vegetable%20Vendor%3A%20Crowdfundi