.com%2FAbbevillePD%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%20on%20Facebook.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Police%20also%20praised%20the%20quick-thinking%20bravery%20of%20the%20church%20congregation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Facebook%20post%2C%20St%20Mary%20Magdalen%20thanked%20its%20parishioners%20and%20police%20for%20%26quot%3Bacting%20quickly%20to%20ensure%20safety%20for%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20uniformed%20police%20will%20be%20at%20all%20upcoming%20Masses%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20is%20investigating%20the%20incident%20alongside%20Abbeville%20Police%20and%20the%20Vermilion%20Parish%20Sheriff's%20Office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715699280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fe9s9uaqg_us-church-_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-teen-armed-with-rifle-attempts-to-storm-church-in-us-arrested-5662139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20ceremony%20was%20underway%2Cparishioners%2C%20including%20parents%20with%20young%20children%2C%20spotted%20the%2016-year-old%20carrying%20the%20rifle%20and%20swarmed%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-teen-armed-with-rifle-attempts-to-storm-church-in-us-arrested-5662139%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-teen-armed-with-rifle-attempts-to-storm-church-in-us-arrested-5662139%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-teen-armed-with-rifle-attempts-to-storm-church-in-us-arrested-5662139%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20arrests%20Dheerj%20Wadhawan%20in%20Rs%2034%2C000%20cr%20DHFL%20bank%20loan%20fraud%20probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715697528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F20