om%2Ftopic%2Fjammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0face%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20our%20very%20existence%20because%20of%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20(J%26amp%3BK's%20special%20status%20was%20scrapped%20in%202019)%26quot%3B%2C%20National%20Conference%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fomar-abdullah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOmar%20Abdullah%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20NDTV%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20voting%20in%20Srinagar%20in%20the%20fourth%20phase%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20-%20contesting%20from%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Baramulla%20seat%2C%20which%20votes%20next%20week%20-%20called%20the%20centre's%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20challenge%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20former%20state%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20election%20after%20we%20lost%20our%20constitutional%20safeguards...%20we%20(now)%20face%20a%20threat%20to%20our%20very%20existence%20because%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20removed%20protections%20(regarding)%20our%20identity%2C%20land%2C%20and%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%2C%20revoked%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20offered%20constitutional%20safeguards%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20natives%2C%20including%20restrictions%20on%20jobs%20and%20sale%20of%20land.%20It%20was%20removed%2C%20the%20government%20argued%20in%20Parliament%2C%20to%20facilitate%20development%20in%20the%20former%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20amongst%20the%20weakest%20domicile%20laws%20in%20the%20country.%20Ladakh%20(the%20union%20territory%20created%20after%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20former%20state%20of%20J%26amp%3BK)%20has%20stronger%20domicile%20protection%20today...%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20we%20hope%2C%20when%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20restored%20to%20full%20statehood%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20land%20and%20job%20protection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%C2%A0READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-our-battle-not-for-statehood-will-get-it-anyway-omar-abdullah-5647613%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Battle%20Not%20For%20Statehood%2C%20Will%20Get%20It%20Anyway%26quot%3B%3A%20Omar%20Abdullah%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20trying%20to%20unnerve%20anybody%20on%20(the%20issue%20of)%20land%20and%20job%20rights%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20What%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20correct%20and%20based%20on%20reality.%20Today%2C%20or%20tomorrow%2C%20we%20will%20face%20a%20threat%20and%20you%20can't%20deny%20that!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20December%20decision%20-%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20upheld%20the%20government's%20move%20to%20scrap%20Article%20370%20-%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20final%20and%20binding%20(for%20ever)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20ago%2C%20after%20the%20top%20court's%20ruling%20on%20Article%20370%2C%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdisappointed-but-not-disheartened-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-verdict-4652770%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisappointed%20but%20not%20disheartened%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20struggle%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentres-move-to-scrap-special-status-to-j-k-valid-says-supreme-court-on-article-370-4652669%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECentre's%20Move%20To%20Scrap%20Special%20Status%20To%20J%26amp%3BK%20Valid%3A%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%2C%20a%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%