BJP's%20campaign%2C%20I%20would%20say%20they%20look%20nervous...%20whether%20that%20nervousness%20translates%20into%20less%20seats%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20June%204%20(when%20results%20will%20be%20declared)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-hearing-hold-j-k-election-by-september-2024-supreme-court-to-poll-panel-4652621%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Historic%20J%26amp%3BK%20Ruling%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Sets%20Election%20Deadline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20major%20election%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20since%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20big%20ruling%20on%20Article%20370%2C%20in%20which%20the%20court%2C%20crucially%2C%20also%20directed%20the%20conduct%20of%20Assembly%20elections%20latest%20by%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20state%20election%20in%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715694420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4fcos4rk_omar-abdullah-ani_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-article-370-j-k-faces-existential-threat-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-scrapping-5662643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20face%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20our%20very%20existence%20because%20of%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%26quot%3B%2C%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20told%20NDTV%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20voting%20in%20Srinagar%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-article-370-j-k-faces-existential-threat-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-scrapping-5662643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-article-370-j-k-faces-existential-threat-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-scrapping-5662643%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-article-370-j-k-faces-existential-threat-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-scrapping-5662643%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pannun%20Case%20Will%20Not%20Affect%20Ties%20With%20India%3A%20US%20Envoy%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20will%20not%20affect%20India-US%20relationship%2C%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20told%20NDTV%20today.%20Calling%20the%20ties%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20consequential%20relationship%26quot%3B%20passing%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20era%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20likened%20it%20to%20a%20marriage%2C%20with%20its%20inevitable%20fights%20and%20disagreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20we%20manage%20those%20moments%20defines%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20for%20naysayers%20who%20predict%20a%20roadblock%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say...%20our%20work%20every%20single%20day%20at%20the%20embassy%2C%20every%20single%20day%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Washington%2C%20has%20not%20slowed%20down%20one%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20continues%20to%20accelerate%20because%20we%20want%20this%20relationship%2C%20we%20need%20this%20relationship%2C%20and%20we%20have%20this%20relationship%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20had%20alleged%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20murder%20Pannun%2C%20a%20US-based%20Sikh%20separatist.%20The%20state%20department%20had%20alleged%20that%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20plot%20and%20accused%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20the%20US%20is%20doing%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20anti-India%20activities%20by%20Khalistanis%20from%20foreign%20soil%2C%20Mr%20Garcetti%20cited%20diversity%20--%20%26quot%3Breligious%2C%20cultural%20or%20linguistic%26quot%3B%20--%20and%20invoked%20the%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20know%20we%20should%20be%20focusing%20on%20what%20people%20do%20when%20they%20cross%20the%20line%20legal%20behaviour.%20No%20matter%20what%20the%20source%2C%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20accountability.%20What%20people%20say%20can%20be%20disturbing.%20But%20it's%20what%20people%20do%20that%20breaks%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20recent%20controversy%20over%20a%20report%20of%20the%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%2C%20Mr%20Garcetti%20also%20said%20democracy%20and%20diverse%20populations%20are%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20things%20to%20manage%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20living%20without%20them%20is%20not%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20had%20criticised%20the%20report%2C%20saying%20it%20comes%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bbiased%20organisation%20with%20a%20political%20agenda%26quot%3B.%20The%20report%20was%20also%20red-flagged%20by%20Russia%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20an%20example%20of%20the%20US%20interfering%20in%20Indian%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%2C%20in%20the%20annual%20report%2C%20had%20criticised%20India%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20religious%20freedom%20and%20asked%20the%20US%20state%20department%20to%20declare%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BCountry%20of%20Particular%20Concern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20America%20and%20that%20India%20are%20committed%20to%20managing%20the%20diversity%2C%20whether%20that's%20religious%2C%20cultural%20or%20linguistic%20of%20both%20of%20our%20countries%2C%20and%20showing%20that%20we%20live%20in%20democracies%2C%20not%20dictatorships%2C%20where%20we%20are%20free%20to%20speak%20not%20only%20those%20good%20moments%2C%20but%20also%20criticisms%20when%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20US%2C%20he%20suggested%2C%20remains%20on%20the%20side%20of%20caution%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stance%20%26quot%3Bthat%20comes%20from%20a%20place%20of%20humility%20where%20we%20criticise%20our%20own%20selves%20and%20say%2C%20'What%20would%20you%20do%20better'%20%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20this%20independent%20commission%20looks%20all%20around%20the%20world%20at%20instances%20which%20might%20or%20might%20not%20be%20government%20generated.%20They%20might%20just%20be%20between%20communities%2C%20sometimes%20where%20we%20know%20prejudice%20exists%20between%20human%20beings%20and%20we%20highlight%20where%20those%20things%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715693520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhlaj9hvs_us-envoy-eric-garcetti_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkhalistan-terrorist-pannun-case-will-not-affect-ties-with-india-us-envoy-to-ndtv-5662533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20issue%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20will%20not%20affect%20India-US%20relationship%2C%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20told%20NDTV%20today..%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkhalistan-terrorist-pannun-case-will-not-affect-ties-with-india-us-envoy-to-ndtv-5662533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2