said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20overwhelmed%20and%20emotional.%20I%20did%20not%20even%20realise%20how%2010%20years%20passed%20under%20the%20shade%20of%20your%20affection.%20'Aaj%20Maa%20Ganga%20ne%20mujhe%20god%20le%20liya%20hai'%20(today%2C%20Maa%20Ganga%20has%20adopted%20me).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaranasi%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20seventh%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20on%20June%201.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715693340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F78s9r3po_pm-modi-nomination_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-declares-assets-worth-rs-3-02-crore-owns-no-house-or-car-5662534%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20total%20assets%20worth%20over%20Rs%203%20crore%2C%20but%20owns%20no%20land%2C%20houses%20or%20cars%2C%20he%20has%20said%20in%20his%20election%20affidavit.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20filed%20his%20nomination%20from%20the%20Varanasi%20constituency%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-declares-assets-worth-rs-3-02-crore-owns-no-house-or-car-5662534%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-declares-assets-worth-rs-3-02-crore-owns-no-house-or-car-5662534%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-declares-assets-worth-rs-3-02-crore-owns-no-house-or-car-5662534%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Name%20Of%20Indian%20Astronaut%20Set%20For%20Space%20Station%3F%20US%20Envoy%20To%20India%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20astronaut%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20this%20year%2C%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20details%20of%20the%20space%20mission%2C%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20also%20suggested%20the%20name%20of%20the%20astronaut%20who%20will%20fly%20to%20the%20ISS%20on%20an%20American%20mission.%20He%20did%20not%20reveal%20the%20name%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20offer%20that%20was%20made%20by%20the%20President%20was%20to%20put%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20on%20an%20American%20mission%20to%20go%20up%20to%20the%20space%20station%20this%20calendar%20year.%20And%20that's%20still%20the%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garcetti%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20space%2C%20so%20you%20never%20know%2C%20can't%20guarantee%20that%20it%20will%20happen%2C%20but%20we%20do%20expect%20it%20to%20happen.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20indicated%20who%20that%20astronaut%20is.%20I'll%20let%20them%2C%20you%20know%2C%20announce%20that%20at%20the%20proper%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ambassador%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Garcetti%20said%20the%20foundation%20behind%20cooperation%20on%20sending%20the%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20the%20ISS%20is%20all%20about%20maintaining%20a%20bilateral%20relationship%20that%20extends%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bseabed%20to%20the%20stars%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20evidence%20will%20be%20seen%20this%20year%2C%20not%20just%20with%20an%20astronaut%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20help%20put%20in%20space%2C%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%2C%20but%20also%20a%20satellite%20that%20we%20hope%20gets%20launched%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNISAR%20(the%20satellite)%20is%20a%20collaboration%20between%20NASA%20and%20ISRO.%20There%20is%20nothing%20that%20speaks%20more%20about%20the%20hopes%20and%20aspirations%20of%20our%20people%2C%20of%20our%20governments%2C%20and%20our%20relationship%20than%20our%20work%20together%20in%20the%20space%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENISAR%20is%20a%20joint%20Earth-observing%20mission%20with%20the%20goal%20to%20make%20global%20measurements%20of%20the%20causes%20and%20consequences%20of%20land%20surface%20changes%20using%20advanced%20radar%20imaging%2C%20the%20mission's%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20NASA%20and%20ISRO%20discussed%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20joint%20radar%20mission%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20this%20goal%20was%20of%20great%20interest%20to%20the%20ISRO%20science%20community.%20ISRO%20identified%20science%20and%20applications%20that%20were%20complementary%20to%20the%20primary%20mission%20objectives%3A%20agricultural%20monitoring%20and%20characterisation%2C%20landslide%20studies%2C%20Himalayan%20glacier%20studies%2C%20soil%20moisture%2C%20coastal%20processes%2C%20coastal%20winds%2C%20and%20monitoring%20hazards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20radar%20frequency%20was%20added%20to%20the%20mission%20to%20better%20fulfil%20these%20science%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENISAR%20will%20be%20the%20first%20satellite%20mission%20to%20use%20two%20different%20radar%20frequencies%20(L-band%20and%20S-band)%20to%20measure%20changes%20in%20the%20planet's%20surface%20less%20than%20a%20centimetre%20across.%20The%20partnership%20with%20India%20has%20been%20key%20to%20preserving%20as%20much%20science%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715691900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fcilkirqo_eric-garcetti_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fname-of-indian-astronaut-set-for-space-station-us-envoy-to-india-eric-garcetti-says-5662367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20astronaut%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20this%20year%2C%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2