-1715149356-300x194.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F70249586_131187284894717_7607123552143147008_n-1715149356-500x323.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F70249586_131187284894717_7607123552143147008_n-1715149356-150x97.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349261%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaharaja%20Sayajirao%20Gaekwad%20III%20started%20the%20concept%20of%20mobile%20libraries%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Facebook%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNagpurBookClub%2Fposts%2Fmaharaja-sayajirao-gaekwad-iii-opened-the-first-mobile-library-in-the-state-of-b%2F131188458227933%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagpur%20Book%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20travelling%20libraries%20are%20common%2C%20and%20a%20loved%20concept.%20But%20over%20130%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20were%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20marvel%2C%20a%20miracle%20if%20you%20will.%20It%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20Gaekwad%20III%20who%20started%20first-of-its-kind%20mobile%20libraries%20when%20he%20introduced%20the%20concept%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20Baroda%20state%20to%20encourage%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20reform%20the%20state%20with%20his%20initiatives.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348905%2Fhydroponics-training-workshop-in-gujarat-india-rasik-nakum-one-farm-hydroponics-rajkot-teaching-soil-less-water-less-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20interesting%20story%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften%20told%20is%20how%20the%20Maharaja%20was%20a%20humble%20boy%20who%20ascended%20the%20throne%20because%20of%20his%20quick%20wit.%20In%201870%2C%20Maharaja%20Khandera