50x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349520%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKabir%20and%20Ahana%20moved%20back%20to%20Kalimpong%20to%20build%20homestay%20of%20their%20dreams.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20ancestral%20land%20and%20farms%20that%20I%20utilised%20to%20make%20a%20farm%20stay%20and%20give%20people%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20culture%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20from%20the%20city%20to%20his%20homeland%20was%20a%20decision%20of%20a%20lifetime.%20Kabir%20took%20the%20leap%20in%202016%2C%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20moved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20move%20was%20soon%20followed%20by%20Ahana%20in%202020.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20have%20ancestral%20land%20in%20a%20great%20location%20to%20begin%20with.%20While%20Kabir%20worked%20on%20building%20the%20property%2C%20I%20worked%20remotely%20to%20market%20the%20property%20before%20finally%20moving%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Palighar%20opened%20its%20gates%20to%20its%20first%20guests.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20homestay%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20happy%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESteeped%20in%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalighar%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20homestay%20that%20smells%20of%20customs%20and%20traditions%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20luxury%20and%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20homestay%20gives%20the%20guests%20is%20an%20authentic%20escape%20from%20their%20city%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKabir%20shares%20that%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20noticed%20how%20the%20houses%20in%20the%20area%20were%20being%20modernised.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old-school%20mud%20homes%20with%20sloping%20bamboo%20roofs%2C%20which%20were%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20area%2C%20were%20all%20gone.%20In%20losing%20our%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20traditional%20culture%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20traditional%20technique%20called%20Irka%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20what%20the%20technique%20involves%20is%20using%20bamboo%2C%20wood%20and%20mud%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20The%20mud%2C%20mixed%20with%20dung%20and%20straw%2C%20is%20plastered%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20woven%20with%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Kabir%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20made%20mud%20bricks%20which%20are%20baked%20in%20the%20sun.%20We%20used%20the%20land%20from%20our%20own%20property%20which%20helped%20us%20reduce%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%20We%20were%20really%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20on%20the%20nature%20around%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ahana%20also%20points%20out%20that%20another%20reason%20to%20use%20mud%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20coolant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20temperatures%20in%20these%20areas%20have%20typically%20been%20low%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20hotter%20days%20now.%20We%20wanted%20to%20use%20a%20method%20that%20keeps%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally%20which%20is%20why%20we%20used%20mud%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20588px)%20100vw%2C%20588px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl