width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20they%20also%20realised%20that%20these%20nutritious%20ice%20creams%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20introduce%20children%20to%20millets%20and%20get%20them%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20this%20traditional%20Indian%20grain!%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20think%20of%20millets%20as%20a%20punishment.%20Research%20shows%20that%20kids%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267083%2Fpapacream-woman-entrepreneur-vegan-ice-cream-engineer-quits-job-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eice%20creams%20and%20shakes%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%2C%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20mode%20to%20introduce%20them%20to%20these%20powerhouses%20of%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20millets%20are%20procured%20from%20their%20own%20farms%2C%20and%20other%20farmers%20in%20Theni%2C%20Dharmapuri%2C%20and%20Krishnagiri%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20is%20entirely%20self-funded%2C%20with%20each%20of%20the%20four%20founders%20investing%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20savings%20into%20realising%20their%20dream.%20Their%20most%20significant%20hurdle%20post-launch%20has%20been%20the%20widespread%20lack%20of%20awareness%20surrounding%20millets.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20diligently%20engaged%20in%20consumer%20education%20initiatives%2C%20conducting%20awareness%20campaigns%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20create%20customer%20awareness.%20We%20started%20visiting%20schools%20and%20colleges%20to%20educate%20the%20youth%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20nutritious%20eating%20habits.%20We%20believe%20that%20knowledge%20is%20the%20key%20to%20transformation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shashidhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20take%20students%20on%20a%20factory%20tour%20to%20show%20them%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20In%202023%2C%20they%20established%20a%20factory%20in%20Trichy%2C%20with%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20opened%20outlets%20in%20Hyderabad%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Equality%20and%20one%20in%20Rajahmundry.%20They%20are%20poised%20to%20launch%2010%20to%2012%20more%20outlets%20in%20the%20coming%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20community%20engagement%20is%20equally%20important.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20treasures%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20adapted%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20an%20increasing%20shift%20towards%20millets%2C%20this%20is%20a%20novel%20way%20to%20include%20them%20in%20our%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E