rrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347983%2Fdosa-origin-story-bengaluru-butter-masala-dosa-history-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20central%20to%20their%20lives%2C%20gratis%20her%20Punjabi%20genes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99d%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20while%20having%20our%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20Indian%20flatbread)%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20already%20be%20planning%20our%20lunch%20menu.%20During%20lunch%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20plan%20for%20evening%20snacks%20and%20while%20having%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%E2%80%99d%20discuss%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Sundays%2C%20the%20menu%20was%20non-negotiable.%20The%20spot%20on%20the%20table%20was%20reserved%20for%20%3Cem%3Emutton%20biryani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20comprising%20meat%20cooked%20in%20spices%2C%20herbs%20and%20yoghurt%2C%20served%20with%20rice).%20And%20as%20the%20family%20gathered%20to%20feast%2C%20bonds%20were%20formed%2C%20laughs%20were%20shared%2C%20jokes%20were%20cracked%2C%20and%20memories%20were%20etched%20onto%20a%20young%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5hXwn_SsBe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5hXwn_SsBe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%