E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20started.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20dish%20Saigal%20prepares%20has%20a%20sensory%20richness%20to%20it%20%E2%80%94%20sight%2C%20smell%20and%20taste%20compete%20to%20thrill%20the%20judges.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20I%20would%20watch%20the%20show%20with%20my%20twins%2C%20I%20always%20found%20it%20to%20be%20so%20wholesome%3B%20a%20great%20bonding%20experience%3B%20something%20to%20come%20home%20to.%20I%20would%20watch%20in%20awe%20as%20the%20judges%20gave%20feedback%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309089%2Fhow-to-start-business-engineer-quits-job-to-start-homecooked-food-startup-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20cooks%20%3C%2Fa%3Edished%20out%20incredible%20things%2C%20and%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20their%20skills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20has%20watched%20Saigal%20grow%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%20and%20she%20credits%20its%20challenges%20for%20boosting%20her%20creativity%20and%20quick%20thinking.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20expressions%20of%20surprise%20you%20see%20are%20all%20real%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20gratitude%20colours%20her%20emotional%20palette%20as%20she%20looks%20back%20on%20her%20journey.%20But%20it%20is%20intriguing%20how%20it%20all%20transpired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20reveals%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20day%20while%20watching%20the%20show%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20screen%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98That%20%5Bthe%20MasterChef%20kitchen%5D%20is%20where%20I%20want%20to%20be.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20up%20your%20mind%20and%20the%20entire%20universe%20will%20conspire%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20this.%3C%2Fp%